>> Start wsl and go preffred directory
  -> In my case it is - /server/www/
 
>>create a folder in windows
  -> in my case it is - /g/development
  
>>got to wsl and run this command
   -> ln -s /mnt/g/development secretProjects
  
  Note: ln                 = link
        -s                 = symbolic link
        /mnt/g/development = actual directory path
        secretProjects     = symbolic link's folder name
